msgctxt "656"
msgid "My Meteor Tackle"
msgstr "La mia Carica Meteora"

msgctxt "44_My Meteor Tackle"
msgid ""
"While in Heat Mode, press <Action:Battle_Heavy_Attack@Combat> <Color:7>again after a <Color:Default><Action:Battle_Heavy_Attack@Combat><Color:7> attack to trigger "
"<Color:7>My Meteor Tackle<Color:Default>. "
" "
"Press <Action:Battle_Normal_Attack@Combat> to knock the enemy down, <Action:Battle_Drop_Weapon@Combat> to throw "
"them, or just crush them against a wall."
msgstr ""
"Quando sei in modalità Furore, premi <Action:Battle_Heavy_Attack@Combat> <Color:7>di nuovo dopo un attacco <Color:Default><Action:Battle_Heavy_Attack@Combat><Color:7> per scatenare "
"<Color:7>La mia Carica Meteora<Color:Default>. "
" "
"Premi <Action:Battle_Normal_Attack@Combat> per atterrare il nemico, <Action:Battle_Drop_Weapon@Combat> per lanciare "
"loro, o semplicemente schiacciali contro un muro."
